      "text": "Because if this was not enforced, nobody would stay alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They knew that they have to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
